Welcome to Holocene Park 
Witness the most advanced species ambulate with their subjugated quadrupeds in this modified natural landscape. Some of them can also be seen training for enhancing their already long lifespans, so that they may one day witness more subjugation of the universe. Meanwhile, smaller species of the period scamper about their natural habitat, unaware that their home is actually under protection from activities of these advanced species, by said species. 
P.S. : Technically, it is an epoch unlike Jurassic which is a period, but Quarternary did not sound good here.
P.P.S : I fear I may be on the road to becoming a misanthrope.
+1 to Misanthropy
